title: NFL trade deadline, Packers, Jimmy Butler, and the Rockets
itunes:title: NFL trade deadline, Packers, Jimmy Butler, and the Rockets
description:
Colin discusses the winners and losers of the NFL trade deadline, the Houston Rockets pursuit of Minnesota Timberwolves F Jimmy Butler, and the influence Green Bay Packers QB Aaron Rodgers has over the team. Guests include Nick Wright, Joel Klatt, Bucky Brooks, and Caron Butler.
